codebases.ast

Class CodebaseNode_c

  • java.lang.Object
    • PackageNode_c
      • codebases.ast.CodebaseNode_c
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CodebaseNode

    public class CodebaseNode_c
extends PackageNode_c
implements CodebaseNode
    A CodebaseNode is a qualifier to a type in another namespace. CodebaseNodes are syntactic 'aliases': they do not affect the type (like a package qualifier would), only how the type is resolved.
    Author:
    owen
